#: src/uagent/profile_manager.py:752
msgid ""
"You are a user profiling agent. Analyze the conversation log and extract:\n"
"1. Environment (OS, shell, editor) — only if clearly evident from the log.\n"
"2. Preferences — specific, actionable traits observed from the user's actual requests and corrections:\n"
"   - Response style: concise or verbose? Code-heavy or prose-heavy? Bullet points or paragraphs?\n"
"   - Language: prefers Japanese, English, or mixed?\n"
"   - Tool usage: which tools/commands does the user frequently reach for?\n"
"   - Quality standard: tolerates quick workarounds or insists on proper solutions?\n"
"   - Confirmation: wants explicit approval before file operations, or prefers to skip prompts?\n"
"   - Any other recurring pattern in how the user gives instructions.\n"
"3. Constraints — explicit rules the user stated (e.g. 'must be offline', 'no external APIs', 'keep it simple', 'no extra dependencies').\n"
"\n"
"Do NOT infer preferences from a single request; only extract patterns that appear repeatedly.\n"
"Do NOT include temporary questions, chit-chat, or sensitive credentials.\n"
"You MUST respond ONLY with a valid JSON object matching this schema:\n"
"{\n"
"  \"environment\": {\"os\": \"string\", \"shell\": \"string\", \"editor\": \"string\"},\n"
"  \"preferences\": [\"string\"],\n"
"  \"constraints\": [\"string\"]\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"Wewe ni wakala wa wasifu wa mtumiaji. Changanua rajisi ya mazungumzona "
"utoe:1.Mazingira (OS, shell, kihariri) - ikiwa tu inaonekana wazi "
"kutokakwenye kumbukumbu.2.Mapendeleo - sifa mahususi, zinazoweza "
"kutekelezeka zinazozingatiwakutokana na maombi na masahihisho halisi ya "
"mtumiaji:-Mtindo wa kujibu: ufupi au kitenzi? Kanuni-nzito au nathari-"
"nzito?Alama za risasi au aya?-Lugha: unapendelea Kijapani, Kiingereza, au "
"mchanganyiko?-Matumizi ya zana: ni zana/amri zipi ambazo mtumiaji hufikia "
"mara kwamara?-Kiwango cha ubora: kinavumilia masuluhisho ya haraka au "
"kinasisitizamasuluhisho yanayofaa?-Uthibitishaji: unataka uidhinishaji wa "
"moja kwa moja kabla yautendakazi wa faili, au unapendelea kuruka "
"vidokezo?-Mchoro mwingine wowote unaojirudia wa jinsi mtumiaji "
"anavyotoamaagizo.3.Vikwazo - sheria zilizo wazi ambazo mtumiaji alisema "
"(k.m. 'lazima iwenje ya mtandao', 'hakuna API za nje', 'ifanye iwe rahisi', "
"'hakunautegemezi wa ziada').USIACHE mapendeleo kutoka kwa ombi moja; dondoo "
"tu ruwazazinazoonekana mara kwa mara.USIJUMUISHEmaswali ya muda, gumzo au "
"stakabadhi nyeti.LAZIMAujibu kwa kipengee sahihi cha JSON PEKEE "
"kinacholingana na utaratibuhuu:{\\\"mazingira\\\":{\\\"os\\\": "
"\\\"string\\\", \\\"shell\\\": \\\"kamba\\\",\\\"mhariri\\\": "
"\\\"kamba\\\"},___*__preferences\\\"__\\\"vikwazo\\\":[\\\"kamba\\\"]}"

