"[INFO] .env.sec content does not match the current startup UAGENT_* "
"environment variables. Use `uag_envsec` to update it."
msgstr ""
"[INFO] Yaliyomo ya .env.sec hayalingani na vigezo vya sasa vya mazingira vya"
" UAGENT_* wakati wa kuanzisha. Tumia `uag_envsec` kuyasasisha."

